### Get all expenses (no auth needed)
GET https://localhost:7091/api/Expense

### Create expense (protected)
POST https://localhost:7091/api/Expense/CreateExpense
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Xyt0Wj2JA5QFmWkqht0lHmRhd4k5F6ggzxH0AKbnFkE

{
    "description": "Test expense",
    "amount": 50.00,
    "categoryId": 1
}

### Update expense (protected)
PUT https://localhost:7091/api/Expense/UpdateExpense/11
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Xyt0Wj2JA5QFmWkqht0lHmRhd4k5F6ggzxH0AKbnFkE

{
    "id": 11,
    "description": "Updated test expense",
    "amount": 75.00,
    "categoryId": 1
}

